# tests.config - configuration for integration tests
#
# These tests exercise live zone transfers between three BreathGSLB
# instances acting as primary, secondary and standby. To run them you
# must provide real server endpoints and TSIG credentials below and
# ensure each server permits AXFR/IXFR from the test host.
#
# Addresses must include an explicit port (usually 53). IPv6 addresses
# should be wrapped in square brackets, e.g. [2001:db8::1]:53.
#
# Uncomment and adjust the following lines for your environment:
# zone=example.org.
# tsig_name=gslb-xfr.
# tsig_secret=base64encodedsecret==
# primary=192.0.2.1:53,[2001:db8::1]:53
# secondary=192.0.2.2:53,[2001:db8::2]:53
# standby=192.0.2.3:53,[2001:db8::3]:53
